window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>From Audie Award winning, </b><b><i>New York Times</i></b><b> best-selling author Kylie Scott comes an irresistible new romance - available in audio first!</b></p> <p>When a vicious attack leaves 25-year-old Clementine Johns with no memory, she’s forced to start over. Now she has to figure out who she was and why she made the choices she did - which includes leaving the supposed love of her life, tattoo artist Ed Larsen, only a month before. </p> <p>Ed can hardly believe it when his ex shows up at his tattoo parlor with no memory of their past, asking about the breakup that nearly destroyed him. The last thing he needs is more heartache, but he can’t seem to let her go again.</p> <p>Should they walk away for good, or does their love deserve a repeat performance?</p>"; 
